However, in 2012 Dart was arrested on terrorist charges. 

Dart, who is married and has a daughter, was arrested as he tried to leave for terrorist training in Pakistan. 

He was converted to Islam by hate preacher Anjem Choudary, who also inspired a plot to attack the London Stock Exchange.

