The court appearance was the last time Robb saw his stepbrother.

Despite his conviction Robb hopes his brother will turn his life around when he is released.

His wife, Ayan Hadi, 31 and from West Acton, was given a one-year suspended jail sentence for failing to give police information about her husband.

